author: abrinke1
body: Back-port of PR #19741 , #19743 , and #20006 into CMSSW_9_2_X.  Intended for deployment in Online DQM as soon as feasible.  Includes changed EMTF data formats and unpacking code for RPC hits, consequent changes to class names in the EMTF emulator, and new EMTF DQM plots.
title: EMTF PR for DQM - August 2017
